latestIgtvVideos.title: I LOST MY HERO !! SECOND WAVE OF COVID IS DANGEROUS
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey everyone!  SPEAD THIS MESSAGE AS MUCH AS YOU CAN 🚨🚨
I never knew mai ye video bnaunga . Its hard to believe that i lost my father on 8th of april due to COVID -19 . This second wave of Covid is really dangerous and you all need to be aware of this . I am seeing alot of people partying all night in the clubs , roaming around unnecessary out there , Trust me it’s really dangerous for your parents if not for you . Ap log soch rhe hogey ki ap young ho and you will recover but you can be the carrier . Keep a check on the oxygen every day and if its dipping, consult a doctor ! 
.
It all started with a Mild fever and nothing else. 
Agar apke ghar mai kisi ko bhi mild fever hai ya koi bhi symptom hai get them tested and admit krvao . Take all the necessary precautions if you are going out . That’s all i want to tell you guys 
.
Stay safe and Stay healthy 🙌🏻
